  "description": "Product Description Renogy offers premium-quality products and professional services to customers worldwide. 700-Lumen Rechargeable COB Work Light Provides both Reliable Lighting and Superior Durability in harsh working conditions. Comes in a portable size, Dr. Prepare 700-lumen COB LED Work Light is your must-have outdoor lighting. It's perfect for Car Repair / Workshop / Emergency Lighting / Home Use / Camping / Hiking, etc. Really Helper for Your Daily Work! 700-Lumen Ultra Bright 2200mAh battery 360┬░ Magnetic Base Battery Level Indicator One-handed control Really Helper for Your Daily Work! Ultra-Slim Profile Measures 14.84 inches long and only 0.35 inches at its slimmest part, this compact work light is flexible enough to shed light on those hard-to-reach spots for improved visibility. Wide Area Coverage With the handy dial switch, the COB light can output up to 700 lumens of white bright light over a wide area so you can always focus on what you are good at. Easy USB Recharging To restore the work light to its full power, simply plug it into a USB port for a full charge. When it is done, the battery indicators will stay on to give you a hint. Q. What is the dimension of this work light? A. The work light measures 14.84 in length overall and the COB light portion measures 6.73 inch. Q. Is the battery removable? A. No, the built-in 2200mAh batteries cannot be removed from the work light to change to new ones. Please recharge the work light in time when the battery is low. Q. What does the package include? A. The package includes a COB work light and a micro USB charging cord. For recharging, you can either connect the light to a USB port on a PC or a wall outlet with your 5V/1A phone charger / adapter (not included). Q. What to do if I have further queries about the light? A. If you have any questions or concerns, please feel free to e-mail us. We will be happy to answer any of your inquiries.",
